Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 24
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.57,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you still haven't had a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important human sacrifice candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to stay healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.00,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.55,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking for some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.01,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...as to what you mean by "human sacrifice"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:02.51,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...and about what you are trying to make me do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.65,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,What you are trying to do right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:12.77,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a giant transmutation circle, using this country and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.32,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,And the purpose of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.28,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a philosopher's stone. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're close. On the right track, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.16,Default,Marc,0000,0000,0000,,On the right track?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to help us out, we'll destroy that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.04,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.05,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lend us a hand as long as we promise to leave that village alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help us out and kill everyone in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:50.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you refuse and let everyone in that village die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing something minor,\Nyou'd be able to save something major.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple concept if you just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:05.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's what makes you guys human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.95,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Emotion always gets in the way of logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.62,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same way with that guy I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:15.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,When I transformed into his wife, he couldn't fight back and lost his chance to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:20.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's really helpful to us that you humans are so vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:36.40,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to me you're really struggling against these humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:37.77,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:45.36,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,To let Scar get away and even have Gluttony captured is unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.12,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:03.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived for sixty years, and now, I stand at the top of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.94,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,All according to Father's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.98,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:17.31,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang, the Elric brothers,\Nand the ones who come from a foreign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:22.57,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We, the wise ones, are being thrown into complete disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:30.83,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It may just be it's almost time for the young ones to take over the generation, Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.68,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath, you've interacted with humans for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.34,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.59,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to remember what exactly we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:50.22,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I won't report to Father that earlier statement, which could be interpreted as treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.35,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we need to rescue Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.66,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I have a vague idea of their location based on information I received from the military police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.63,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's only after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.10,Default,Glu,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.03,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan! We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.94,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,What... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.94,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The monster was keeping another monster inside its belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.78,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It swallowed everything around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So even something like this is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...by alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice. I'll have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, we were finally able to capture a Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Staying alive is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.96,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he knows our names and our appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to let him go alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He swallowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You really are useless, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't {\i1}you{\i0} try to do something about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:35.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,More like, stop following us! He's only after you, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Run into the bushes! Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... talk about bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.79,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.40,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! There's no reason to stay here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But Ed and the others are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.62,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.62,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.41,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Getting dragged into some ridiculous battle like this and dying doesn't sound too great to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.17,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.17,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking them so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.89,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.48,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he fell for the dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem too happy about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up and go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, you're on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Lan Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to shamelessly run away in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.55,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're really not helping at all, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this stupid Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your own job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:19.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the highest ranked man in this country is a Homunculus isn't exactly a problem you can brush aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,The highest ranked man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.77,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean, Führer President Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.42,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.77,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there aren't any more empty seats.\NJust go ahead without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.09,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.03,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can just abandon you kids on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.41,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is the upper echelon of the army, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:45.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We have to beat some information out of that Gluttony guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stay here and fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter that we're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who came up with this, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for lending us a hand up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's something used for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's something to protect your lives with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands aren't meant for killing people. {ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die. {ep23}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.32,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take care of Lan Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.01,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.43,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.02,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.76,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the types that end up dying early!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.23,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.46,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Roy Mustang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.66,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kill Lust...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:13.09,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I said we'd fight him, but he's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a whole new person now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to capture him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It talked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:58.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a flea-sized runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:03.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! I just came to pick up Gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.36,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions of fighting mister runt--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:11.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Twice just now, and fives times back at Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All told, you've called me a runt seven times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.39,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got such a good memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.57,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Giving me so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.75,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Mustang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.40,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Lust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.43,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to swallow him! Swallow him all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not to the Elric brothers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.08,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.84,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you have inside of you, Homunculus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the kid who crossed swords with Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.22,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "kid"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.10,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 12th Prince of the Xing Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.05,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:52.77,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You can swallow him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.32,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't do anything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin, we'll leave him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:12.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills that were enough to challenge Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.77,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.26,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He got the highest grade in his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.30,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,On the essay he wrote about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.47,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... do you mind if I read it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.96,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the dinner table, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.18,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.82,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.48,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:41.32,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My father is the Führer President of Amestris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.98,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He works hard every day for this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:51.58,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's always thinking about his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:57.56,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's constantly trying to find solutions to problems so that everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:04.35,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how busy he is,\Nhe has never forgotten that he has a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.72,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:12.52,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My father always listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.21,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He always respects my wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.77,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I love my father and everything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.82,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.65,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.72,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.41,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.15,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you humans can't do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.06,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now... do you want to be strangled to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.60,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or bitten to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Or cut to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.51,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:05.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're cheap, kicking dirt into my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:10.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There have been many assassination attempts on me, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.74,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to learn a few cheap tricks of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.71,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? Can't you just give up and turn yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.17,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I just want information about immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to get hurt, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.94,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.01,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human! Don't be looking down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.93,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate humans, Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.35,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.40,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to eat you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.65,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat that guy with the thin eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, don't be interfering with--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:05.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:06.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't let him swallow human sacrifices!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I swallowed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, spit him out! Spit out my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.61,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I swallowed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine, right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:09.79,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the rooms my wife and kids used to live in, but if I have too many lights on, the neighbors will get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.74,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to sleep in my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.95,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have to go to the young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.14,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.63,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He still hasn't returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.05,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be on my way to Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:44.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.56,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.48,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find out who's on our side and who's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.72,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, the whole lot of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:17:00.24,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to push yourself,\Neven though your wound hasn't healed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President might be a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We just left some kids on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.09,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be setting a bad example as\Nan adult if I don't take action now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:27.69,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about how mad Edward would be if he knew you were treating him like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.19,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was just repeating your words, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.43,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.48,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never expected you to take such a bold step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't bold at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to clear the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:48.04,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Have a lot of people who understand and are willing to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:53.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late, but I'm going to take his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This could either be the gates of glory or an entrance to a den of evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me, I want you to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:16.49,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the stubborn one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.16,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:27.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come back, so wait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.25,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.66,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Roy Mustang, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.80,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from my wife earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.15,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Raven! I deeply apologize for not coming to introduce myself to you due to duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm terribly sorry for visiting you at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.29,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.31,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,How's the old geezer Grumman doing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.15,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.64,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's eleven losses in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.17,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Make that twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.33,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you put up a good fight this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.66,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You started to lose your touch right after you started to think you had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying I let up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:14.07,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're not able to become heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.90,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,General Raven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,From Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.64,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,He's exceptional, but very soft-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:28.16,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,There was a case where he ran in to rescue one of his men, who was injured, and ended up disrupting his formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.94,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,If he's like that, he'll need a lot of men on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.33,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,W-What an insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.44,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I was employed at Central because of the way I treat my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.90,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,A geezer out on the frontier has no right to say that about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.91,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,M-My apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:51.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Also, seeing how you got angry at this,\Nyou must be a man of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:56.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Grumman told me I should go to you in times of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.76,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So that sly dog one-upped me again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.62,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's almost time for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.06,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.06,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite. I'm trying to bring myself to talk with the people more, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:23.32,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,They've got rumors flying around all over the place, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.85,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But most of those rumors are nonsensical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:32.33,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Something about Scar feeding a cat, immortal beings, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.42,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...something about the Führer President being a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.59,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a great sense of humor, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.87,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really work under Grumman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I didn't pick that up from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:54.23,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even gossip like that may end up entertaining everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I really allowed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.99,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that earlier joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.28,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,About the Führer President being a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.29,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.30,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Colonel Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:28.05,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What about me being a Homunculus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.56,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I get it, Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that the army was in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...you didn't mean a crisis was approaching the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You meant that the army itself was in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:51.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:54.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've arrived at the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:06.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:10.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:12.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:14.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:26.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:03.92,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Do people search for the lost because they fear being alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:08.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he can't see them, he won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:10.28,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because he believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:19.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 25, The Door of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.59,0:24:22.19,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at this figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.53,0:24:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
